sentences: Ellen Weiler Stiefler (born June 4, 1958) is an American agent, producer, and lawyer.
Dr. Guarneri's 24 DVD Great Course on the science of natural healing was published by the Teaching Company in October 2012.
Her book, The Heart Speaks, was published by Simon & Schuster in 2006.

Stiefler was a founding board member of Scripps Center for Integrative Medicine Scripps Health - Integrative Medicine and Kids Korps USA Kids Korps USA - Developing Leaders For Life Through Youth Volunteerism and continued to serve on those boards for over a decade.
She founded The Gratitude Foundation in 2003 [1].
